name: Tool fails to express uncertainty in the classification of file recovery results, e.g., where content may be partly overwritten.
references: Hargreaves, C., Nelson, A. and Casey, E., 2024. An abstract model for digital forensic analysis tools-A foundation for systematic error mitigation analysis. Forensic Science International: Digital Investigation, 48, p.301679.
Casey, E., Nelson, A. and Hyde, J., 2019. Standardization of file recovery classification and authentication. Digital Investigation, 31, p.100873.
